item.title: Game for Peace, the Chinese version of PUBG Mobile, launches new "Tomb Burster" ...
item.description:
Game for Peace, the Chinese version of PUBG Mobile, launches new "Tomb Burster" mode on January 27th, following the success of Supernatural Squad in China. Check out the announcement trailer!
